1
00:00:01,875 --> 00:00:05,000
We were not ready for their divine judgment.

2
00:00:05,720 --> 00:00:09,520
We were tested and almost everyone just…

3
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,560
failed.

4
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:21,200
Their dark mysticism shattered an era of enlightenment.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,280
And ushered in the dusk of the 21st century.

6
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:33,640
Billions of lives were lost in a heartbeat.

7
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:39,320
Turned to ash and cast away in the wind.

8
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,520
Our soldiers were gone.

9
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:48,520
But our weapons kept fighting.

10
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:52,062
Driven by an enigma in the networks.

11
00:00:55,560 --> 00:01:00,760
Their surviving forces waged a desperate crusade against the machines.

12
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:07,520
We became bystanders to a relentless war.

13
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:14,000
Now our world is an ever-twisting nightmare.

14
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:19,440
Hellish threats lurk in every whisper and shadow.

15
00:01:23,312 --> 00:01:25,120
There is no glory.

16
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,120
Only survival.

17
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:32,040
Deliver us from this trial.

18
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:36,360
Reclaim our world.

19
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,440
For mankind.

